IMMEDIATE
No.55/4/CF-66 (1)
GOVERNMENI OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Depar tment of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 15th January 1966.
The undersigned is directed to state that, with effect
from the forenoon of January 15, 1966,
(1) Shri Mahavir Tyagi relinquished the office
of Minister of Rehabilitation; and
(i1) Shri Mehr Chand Khanna, Minister of Works &
Housing, assumed charge temporarily of the
Minis try of Rehabilitation in addition to
his present charge of the Ministry of Works
& Housing.
(D.P. Chepra)
for Cabinet Secretary.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the Prime Minister/
the Private Secretary to the Prime Minister, for information.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Private Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/Chairman,
Railway Board/Secretary, Election Commission, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Ministries of the Government of
India/Iok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sa bha Secretariat, for
information.
Deampa
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
"MANOCHA"
